y empirical evidence. Second, these justifications must receive\ndemocratic public review and approval before the agency can adopt the\nalgorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 18:58:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 2021 18:08:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 16:30:15 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 24 Oct 2022 14:48:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-25"}
