hms for\nthis primitive in the Supported-CONGEST model, almost-optimal algorithms in\n(standard) CONGEST, as well as a very simple algorithm for bounded-treewidth\ngraphs with slightly worse bounds. This primitive can be readily used to\naccelerate the FOCS`21 Laplacian solver. We believe this primitive will find\nfurther independent applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Sep 2021 01:45:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Feb 2022 07:29:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 14 May 2022 13:52:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-19"}
