ading term in the low temperature incommensurate spin-spiral\nmagnetic phase. These new findings provide important information for the\nunderstanding of the complex interplay between the magnetic and the structural\norder throughout the $R$Mn$_2$O$_5$ series of type-II multiferroics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Sep 2021 02:37:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-22"}
