cal power previous findings that turning acts to gate mechanosensory\nevoked reversals. Compared to previous approaches, the current system offers\ntargeted optogenetic stimulation to specific body regions or behaviors with\nmany-fold increases in throughput to better constrain quantitative models of\nsensorimotor processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Sep 2021 15:30:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-01"}
